10
00:00:35,790 --> 00:00:37,040
That's true.

11
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:40,210
Then, he must be the one
using it personally.

12
00:00:42,700 --> 00:00:44,240
Let's try replying to him.

13
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:50,720
(Contact me. Xu Yiqing, where are you?)

14
00:00:55,470 --> 00:00:56,570
Let's wait a bit.

15
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:02,040
Just waiting like this won't work.

16
00:01:02,270 --> 00:01:04,050
What if he never replies?

17
00:01:07,950 --> 00:01:09,050
This way.

18
00:01:09,750 --> 00:01:12,210
I'll ask a friend who works in IT.

19
00:01:12,550 --> 00:01:14,850
Let's see if they can help us

20
00:01:15,670 --> 00:01:16,800
track the login location.

21
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:20,490
I'll think about it.

22
00:01:23,910 --> 00:01:26,850
Mr. Gu, someone has filed
a real-name report.

23
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:28,440
I have no choice.

24
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:36,440
According to the time
the photo was taken,

25
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:38,360
it was shortly after this

26
