but that was because
of her outstanding workability,

35
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:04,410
which made her suitable
for the position after the transfer.

36
00:02:04,550 --> 00:02:05,970
Ms. Ling also signed off on it.

37
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:08,320
Mr. Gu,

38
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:10,139
the key issue is,

39
00:02:10,140 --> 00:02:13,650
the whistle-blower is demanding
to disclose the real name,

40
00:02:14,230 --> 00:02:18,200
and the whistle-blower
is the party involved, Xia Xiaoqing.

41
00:02:30,110 --> 00:02:31,200
Miss Xia,

42
00:02:31,510 --> 00:02:32,859
according to protocol,

43
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:35,080
